1474
01:00:05,400 --> 01:00:08,240
Yeah, well, you know,
I just thought I'd ask.

1475
01:00:08,280 --> 01:00:10,480
I owe it to CeeCee and the kids.

1476
01:00:10,520 --> 01:00:11,800
I'm sorry.

